			    </div>

			    <div class="cbp-caption-activeWrap">
			      <div class="cbp-l-caption-body">
			      	<p>Probate is the court-supervised process of settling a person's estate after their death. The property of the deceased is collected, any owed debts and taxes are paid, and the remaining assets are distributed to the heirs. If there is a will, once it is ruled valid, the assets will be distributed as intended. If there is not a will, the state will follow its own process for distributing the assets.</p>

